1. Purpose and Explanation of the app

The SPLASH APP is a weather app which helps people to see the weather for the upcoming week. The weather app offers features that allows the user to see the weather for the next day, it is easier to use this app when users prefer using their phones to check weather predictions.

Throughout this app a simple design is used, it allows users to navigate to different screens and users may use buttons that take them to the desired outcome. Accessibility ensures that the app is useable which makes the app more understanding.

**Content**\- Necessary elements are included to make the app function good. This makes it easier for the user to use the app without any complications. When elements are in place and order it makes the app run smooth with no difficulties.

**Legible Text Content-** Content is legible making it easy for users to read what is being displayed. With a readable font size users will not struggle to see what they’re reading.

**Buttons**\- Each button is in a position where it can be easily accessed by users, users should just know what button to use. Users can see and touch the buttons on the screen with no complications.
